title: Websprint
description:
We are excited to announce the launch of our WebSprint Program, a focused and intensive training initiative designed to empower aspiring developers with full-stack web development skills. This program covers both frontend and backend technologies, enabling participants to build complete, scalable, and professional web applications.

Participants will work on real-world projects, guided by industry experts, while learning modern tools and frameworks such as React, Node.js, Express, MongoDB, Git, RESTful APIs, and more.
